'''''au-''''' means "without" in [[Quenya]]. It is the adjectival form of ''[[ú-]]''.<ref name=PE>{{PE|Eldarin}}, p.144</ref> '''au''' could also be used as an adjective meaning "off, away, not here, of position".<ref name=PE/>
==Etymology==
'''au-''' derives from the prefix '''ú-''' from [[root]] [[Ū]].<ref name=PE/>
==Example==
* '''aunote(a)''' = "not counted, uncounted"<ref name=PE/>
* '''auvane(a)''' = "without beauty"<ref name=PE/>
